text: Ralph Schwarz (28 March 1967 - 17 September 1992) was a Dutch rower. He competed in the men's coxless four event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1967 births Category:1992 deaths Category:Dutch male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of the Netherlands Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:People from Nieuwkoop
